My first paragliding experience at Bir Billing, Asia's highest paragliding point, was truly unforgettable! It was totally worth it. The highlight was the 360° stunt I added to my package, which gave me a thrilling roller coaster-like experience. 

The view from the sky was absolutely breathtaking. 😍😍

This was my ZNMD moment! 🫶🏻✨

Our third stop was truly an unforgettable experience—watch the video all the way through to see why! The journey was exhausting, but 100% worth it. The highlight of our time there was staying in two incredible places. The first was a cozy tree house, and I’ll reveal the second one in the next video. 

Keep showing your love for the Himachal series! ❤️❤️

Btw, I tried Pahadi Dhatu for the first time. Aap sab batayein, kaisa lag raha hai aur sahi pehena hai ya nahi? This was the best property we stayed at during our trip! Keep guessing the location in the comments.
